Effects: Colon moves properly, Aids colon elimination, improves spinal elasticity.', true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'à¤¦à¥à¤µà¤¿à¤ªà¤¾à¤¦à¤µà¤¿à¤ªà¤°à¥€à¤¤à¤¦à¤£à¥à¤¡à¤¾à¤¸à¤¨', 'Two-Legged Pose Dedicated to Koundinya', 'In Dwi Pada Koundinyasana, the deep engagement of Serratus Anterior protracts the scapulae, stabilizing the shoulder joint as the humerus internally rotates to support the legs; simultaneously, rectus abdominis and psoas major work eccentrically to control spinal extension while lifting the frontal iliac spines to maintain balance.', 'A single hairline traces concentric arcs, symbolizing the pose''s complex interplay of opposing forces and the grounded yet expansive nature of advanced asana practice.', true, '/storage/v1/object/public/yoga-cards/158_master_dwi_pada_koundinyasana.webp', '/storage/v1/object/public/audio-assets/158_dwipadakoundinyasana.mp3', NULL, NULL, 7, '{"flow": 5, "long": 60, "short": 15, "standard": 30}', '[]', false),
	('Simhasana II', '050', 'Sá»‹mhÄsana II', 'Final: 110, 111 | Int: 110, 111', 6, false, 137, 107, 'Sit in Padmasana. Place palms on the floor. Stand on your knees. Push your pelvis toward the floor. Open your mouth. Stretch your tongue out.', '02_Seated_and_Lotus_Variations', NULL, NULL, 'Lion Pose II', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Simhasana Two or Lion Pose Two
