Effects: Blessing for arthritis, works dorsal/lumbar spine, supplemental for stiff backs.', true, NULL, NULL, '33', '71 | I, 72', 'à¤­à¤°à¤¦à¥à¤µà¤¾à¤œà¤¾à¤¸à¤¨', 'Bharadvaja''s Pose', 'Bharadvajasana I involves a deep spinal twist initiated from the navel, coupled with the grounding of the ischial tuberosities. This pose requires significant internal rotation of the thighs and the engagement of the deep core muscles to maintain stability and length in the spine.', 'The symbol for Bharadvajasana I features a diagonal slash bisecting a hexagonal vertex. The slash signifies the twisting action of the spine, while the hexagon represents the grounding and stability required in the pose.', true, '/storage/v1/object/public/yoga-cards/112_master_bharadvajasana_i.webp', '/storage/v1/object/public/audio-assets/112_bharadvajasanai.mp3', 72.00, 'I', 6, '{"flow": 5, "long": 60, "short": 15, "standard": 30}', '125', false),
