	('Laghuvajrasana', '176', 'LaghuvajrÄsana', 'Final: 513', 23, false, 372, 309, 'Kneel on the floor. Inhale to lift the torso. Extend the spine upward. Begin to arch the back deeply. Keep the thighs and glutes engaged. Lower the head toward the feet. Rest the crown of the head on the soles or near the heels. Place the hands on the knees. Alternatively, place the hands on the feet or ankles for support. Lift the chest. Push the hips forward. Hold the posture. Exhale to slowly come up.', '09_Backbends', NULL, NULL, 'Little Thunderbolt Pose', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Laghuvajrasana or Little thunderbolt
