	('Salabhasana', '025', 'ÅšalabhÄsana', 'Final: 60 | Int: 61', 1, false, 99, 73, 'Lie full length on your stomach. Face downwards. Stretch your arms back. Exhale completely. Lift your head simultaneously. Lift your chest simultaneously. Lift your legs off the floor simultaneously. Lift them as high as possible. Keep only the abdominal front portion of your body resting on the floor. Bear your weight on this area. Contract your buttocks. Stretch your thigh muscles. Keep both legs fully extended. Keep both legs straight. Stay in the position. Breathe normally.', '01_Standing_and_Basic', NULL, NULL, 'Locust Pose', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Salabhasana or Locust Pose
