	('Eka Hasta Bhujasana', '124', 'Eka Hasta BjujÄsana', 'Final: 344', 5, true, 278, 226, 'Place the leg on the back of the upper arm. Bring the hands to the floor. Spread the fingers wide apart. Press the palms firmly into the floor. Draw the lower belly in. Lift the hips off the floor. Extend the opposite leg straight out. Balance the body on the palms. Hold the pose.', '07_Arm_Balances', NULL, NULL, 'One-Handed Arm Balance', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Eka Hasta Bhujasana or Single hand-arm pose
