	('Eka Pada Viprarita Dandasana II', '179', 'Eka PÄda ViparÄ«ta Dáº¡á¹‡dÄsana II', 'Final: 523 | Int: 522', 29, true, 378, 314, 'Start in Viparita Dandasana. Keep your shoulders strong. Bend your back to capacity. Walk your feet closer to your head. Catch one ankle with your hand. Lift your other leg up towards the ceiling. Maintain balance in the pose. Align your hips. Ensure your back ribs lift upward. Extend the lifted leg fully. Hold the pose for several breaths. Quiet your mind. Release the pose carefully.', '09_Backbends', NULL, NULL, 'One-Legged Inverted Staff Pose II', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Eka Pada Viprarita Dandasana II or One-leg inverted staff II
