Effects: Strenuous abdominal and spinal exercise.', true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'à¤à¤• à¤ªà¤¾à¤¦ à¤µà¤¿à¤ªà¤°à¥€à¤¤ à¤¦à¤£à¥à¤¡à¤¾à¤¸à¤¨', '"One Foot Inverted Staff Pose II": eka (one), pada (foot), viparita (inverted), danda (staff), asana (pose).', 'The pose demands maximal spinal extension and engagement of the quadriceps of the weight-bearing leg for stability. Adductor engagement of the lifted leg promotes internal rotation and hip alignment.', 'Within a square frame, a single angled line ascends from the bottom left to the top right, representing the spine. A small open circle rests on the line, slightly off-center, symbolizing the single point of balance.', true, '/storage/v1/object/public/yoga-cards/179_master_eka_pada_viparita_dandasana_ii.webp', '/storage/v1/object/public/audio-assets/179_ekapadavipraritadandasanaii.mp3', NULL, NULL, 9, '{"flow": 5, "long": 60, "short": 15, "standard": 30}', '[]', false),
