	('Gomukhasana', '037', 'GomukhÄsana', 'Final: 80, 81', 2, true, 114, 87, 'Sit on the floor. Bend the left knee back. Sit on the left foot. Place the right thigh over the left one. Raise the left arm over the head. Bend the left arm at the elbow. Place the left palm below the nape of neck. Lower the right arm. Bend the right arm at the elbow. Raise the right forearm up behind the back. Clasp the hands. Hold the pose for thirty to sixty seconds.', '02_Seated_and_Lotus_Variations', '', NULL, 'Cow Face Pose', NULL, 'Gomukhasana
