	('Virabhadrasana III', '009', 'VÄ«rabhadrÄsana III', 'Final: 17 | Int: 16', 5, true, 73, 50, 'Stand in Virabhadrasana I on the right side. Exhale, bend the trunk forward. Rest the chest on the right thigh. Simultaneously lift the left leg. Straighten the right leg. Keep the body and left leg parallel to the floor. Extend arms forward reaching into them. Turn the left heel toward the ceiling. Cut the outer seam of the standing leg back. Stay in the pose for 20 seconds. Develop harmony and poise. The pose provides vigor for runners.', '01_Standing_and_Basic', NULL, NULL, 'Warrior III Pose', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Virabhadrasana III or Warrior III
