	('Urdhva Kukkutasana', '154', 'Åªrdhva KukkutÄsana', 'Final: 417, 418, 419 | Int: 413, 414, 415, 416', 18, false, 320, 265, 'Assume Lotus Pose. Enter Headstand Two. Transition from Headstand Two to an arm balance on the hands. Tighten the arms and shoulders. Extend the arms fully. Maintain balance on the hands. Move the torso up and down. Support the crossed legs with your arms. Hold the final pose.', '08_Advanced_Leg_behind_Head', NULL, NULL, 'Upward Rooster Pose', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Urdhva Kukkutasana or Upward cock pose
