	('Marichyasana I', '064', 'MarÄ«chyÄsana I', 'Final: 144 | Int: 143', 5, true, 159, 126, 'Sit in Dandasana. Extend one leg straight forward. Bend the other knee. Place the bent foot flat on the floor close to the hip. Wrap the arm around the bent knee. Clasp the hands behind the back. Inhale and lengthen the torso. Exhale and fold the torso forward. Bring the chin toward the straight knee. Stay in the pose. Release the hands. Straighten the bent leg. Return to Dandasana.', '03_Forward_Bends', '', NULL, 'Marichiâ€™s Pose I', NULL, 'Marichyasana I
