	('Setu Bandhasana Sarvangasana', '098', 'Setu BandhÄsana SarvÄngÄsana', 'Final: 259 | Int: 256, 257, 258', 10, false, NULL, NULL, 'Begin in Sarvangasana, keeping your palms firmly pressed against your back. Bend your knees to bring your heels toward your buttocks, then lift your chest and spine upward. On an exhalation, lower your legs backward until your feet reach the floor.

