	('Swastikasana', '229', 'SvastikÄsana', 'Final: 5, 6', 1, false, NULL, NULL, 'Sit on the floor with legs extended. Bend the left leg and place the sole against the right inner thigh. Bend the right leg and place the foot between the left thigh and calf muscle, so the feet are locked between the thighs and calves. Keep the spine, neck, and head erect. Rest the hands on the knees in Jnana Mudra or place them in the lap. Maintain a steady and comfortable posture while breathing naturally.', NULL, 'A stable meditative seat; ensure the heels are not pressing against the pubic bone.', NULL, 'Auspicious Pose', '14/2/2026 4:12pm', 'Swastikasana (Auspicious Pose)
