	(4, 'Surya Namaskar Classical', '225 | 10 | [] Pranamasana | Action: Exhale, palms to heart. Focus: Settle the breath.
226 | 10 | [] Hasta Uttanasana | Action: Inhale, sweep arms overhead. Focus: Lift ribs; look slightly up.
020 | 12 | [] Uttanasana | Action: Exhale, fold forward. Focus: Relax neck; hands to floor.
227 | 12 | [] Ashwa Sanchalanasana | Action: Inhale, step Right leg back, knee down. Focus: Open chest forward. side:R
033 | 12 | [] Adho Mukha Svanasana | Action: Exhale, step Left leg back. Focus: Lift hips high; press floor away.
228 | 8 | [] Ashtanga Namaskara | Action: Hold breath/Exhale, drop knees, chest, and chin. Focus: Elbows in.
031 | 12 | [] Bhujangasana | Action: Inhale, slide forward and lift chest. Focus: Shoulders down; open heart.
033 | 12 | [] Adho Mukha Svanasana | Action: Exhale, lift hips back. Focus: Stretch heels down; lengthen spine.
227 | 12 | [] Ashwa Sanchalanasana | Action: Inhale, step Right leg forward, back knee down. Focus: Sink hips; lift heart. side:L
020 | 10 | [] Uttanasana | Action: Exhale, step Left leg forward and fold. Focus: Let the head hang heavy.
226 | 10 | [] Hasta Uttanasana | Action: Inhale, sweep arms overhead to stand. Focus: Reach through fingertips.
