Asanas should be preferably practiced on an empty stomach. Tea, coffee, milk proceeding practices not harmful however an hour should lapse if one has had light meal and four hours after full meals before practice. Light beverages may be taken after asanas but one hour should elapse before solid foods are eaten. Solid foods taken immediately after practice may harm digestion.

